### Output configuration
output * bg ~/Pictures/Wallpapers/castle_in_the_sky.jpg fill
output eDP-1 resolution 1920x1080 position 0,1081
output DP-2  resolution 1920x1080 position 0,0

### Gaps and egdes
smart_gaps on
gaps inner 10
default_border pixel 2 
focus_follows_mouse no


### Palette
set $black    #343434ff
set $gray     #06989aff
set $lred     #eeeeecff
set $blue     #254775ff
set $lblue    #8ac4d3ff
set $white    #eeeeecff

# Color                   border    background text    indicator  child_border
  client.focused          $lblue    $black     $gray   $lblue     $lblue
  client.focused_inactive $gray     $black     $gray   $gray      $gray
  client.unfocused        $black    $black     $gray   $black     $blue
  client.urgent           $lred     $black     $gray   $lred      $lblue

for_window [app_id="quickfile"] floating enable
for_window [app_id="quickfile"] border none 
for_window [class="jetbrains-idea"] border none 
for_window [class="Inkscape"] border none 

### Input configuration
